What is the treatment for comatose patients?

   Follow
   2 answers 2
   Report Abuse
   Are you sure that you want to delete this answer? (BUTTON) Yes (BUTTON)
   No

   IFRAME:
   [99]https://dmros.ysm.yahoo.com/ros/?c=127093da&w=678&h=315&ty=noscript
   &tt=What is the treatment for comatose
   patients?&r=yahoo%2C+answers%2C+questions%2C+Health%2CDiseases+%26+Cond
   itions%2CRespiratory+Diseases

